item.title: CVE-2018-14796|2024-09-17T02:21:06.554Z -- tec4data -- smartcooler
item.description: Tec4Data SmartCooler, all versions prior to firmware 180806, the device responds to a remote unauthenticated reboot command that may be used to perform a denial of service attack.
